Personal Notes:
A game that has reinstilled a love for video games. I've seriously had my faith in the future of this medium through this game.
A bit step up from P4, which is so impressive in its own right, considering P4 being great already. Loads of content. I feel 100% is an underestimate currently. Multiple runs through this is going to be a long time, especially given how it's enjoyable to savor every bit of dialogue, fighting, and order of operations; chasing perfection in a limited time, constantly.
